If you&rsquo;ve not had the joy of running into this particular error: https://github.com/numpy/numpy/issues/15947 I don&rsquo;t envy you.
There&rsquo;s quite a lot of information on the GitHub issue thread about it and on stack overflow etc and honestly you should look at that for a better explanation, those people know far more than me!
